\q3 long alta bilong yu. 
\c 52
\s Man i amamas long pasin nogut, em i olsem longlong man
\s2 Devit i raitim dispela song, em kain song ol i kolim Maskil. Devit i raitim dispela song long taim Doek bilong kantri Idom i go long Sol na i tokim em olsem, “Devit i go long haus bilong Ahimelek.”
\q1
\v 1 Yu \x - \xo 52 Het tok \xt 1 Sml 22.9-10\x* strongpela man,
\q2 bilong wanem yu bikmaus
\q2 na yu amamas nating
\q3 long pasin nogut yu bin mekim
\q4 long ol manmeri bilong God?
\q2 Oltaim God i save marimari long ol.
\q1
\v 2 Yu \x - \xo 52.2 \xt Sng 50.19, 59.7, 64.3\x* man bilong giaman,
\q2 tok bilong yu
\q3 i olsem resa i sap moa,
\q2 na i katim nogut narapela man.
